name: MySQL5

getPSDEDataQueryCodeConds.customCond:
EXISTS(SELECT * FROM `res_groups_users_rel` t21 
 WHERE 
 t1.`ID` = t21.`GID`  AND  ( t21.`USER_ID` = #{ctx.datacontext.user_id} ) )
getPSDEDataQueryCodeConds.name: 查询条件

queryCode:
SELECT
t1.`API_KEY_DURATION`,
t1.`CATEGORY_ID`,
t11.`NAME` AS `CATEGORY_NAME`,
t1.`COLOR`,
t1.`CREATE_DATE`,
t1.`CREATE_UID`,
t1.`ID`,
t1.`NAME`,
t1.`SHARE`,
t1.`WRITE_DATE`,
t1.`WRITE_UID`
FROM `res_groups` t1 
LEFT JOIN `ir_module_category` t11 ON t1.`CATEGORY_ID` = t11.`ID`
